@startuml
!theme plain
title 20. CXL Pools for UA-Link Pods
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName DejaVu Sans
left to right direction

rectangle "UA-Link pod" as N1 #D6EAF8
rectangle "CXL pool manager" as N2 #D5F5E3
rectangle "CXL memory devices" as N3 #FCF3CF
rectangle "Coherence warm KV" as N4 #E8DAEF
rectangle "Scheduler gates" as N5 #FADBD8

N1 --> N2 : pod locality
N2 --> N3 : ownership epoch
N3 --> N4 : memory capacity
N4 --> N5 : warm state

note bottom
Actor-facing contract: lower-layer resource identifiers remain hidden unless the ADR explicitly defines them as operator-only evidence.
end note
@enduml
